#<AdxTL>@(#)0.0.0.0 $Revision$ 
#PUNTO ENTRADA CFMDLVFIL: Solo validar entregas planta 900 si NAEKO ha confirmado entrega (campo ZSTANAEKO = 4)

$ACTION
Case ACTION
  When "CFMDLVFIL"     :   Gosub CFMDLVFIL
Endcase
Return

$CFMDLVFIL
If [M]STOFCY="900"
   FILSUP-='& ZSTANAEKO=4' 
Endif
If [M]STOFCY=""
   FILSUP-='& ((STOFCY="900" & ZSTANAEKO=4) OR (STOFCY<>"900"))' 
Endif
Return